snippet.title: Rocket Arena - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It’s time to wake up and smell the rocket fuel. Launch into an extraordinary world where rockets rule everything. Crater welcomes you on July 14 http://x.ea.com/63474

Who knew a world where rockets are everywhere could be so fun? Get ready to launch into explosive 3v3 action. Choose your hero and join the Rocket Championship Tour -- where the most skilled rocket competitors in the land battle it out for the Crater Cup. Master your hero’s unique rockets and abilities to rule the arena and become a champion! And there’s plenty more heroes, maps, and rocket-y rewards to come -- Season One launches July 28. Soon you’ll be seeing rockets everywhere too.

Did we mention there are rockets?

Pre-order now on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin and Steam for PC: http://x.ea.com/63475

Follow us on:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/RocketArena
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rocketarena
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rocketarena
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJ8gEWetIo9rmic8Ss4rpiA
Discord: https://discord.gg/rocketarena
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/RocketArena/

#RocketArena #RocketEverywhere #WelcomeToCrater
